    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.22.29" />
                <note type="curatorial">29-1</note>
                <fw type="curatorial">29</fw>
                
             <fw type="letterhead">   
                <del><hi rend="caps">UNIVERSITY OF MISSOURI</hi></del>
                 <lb/>
                <hi rend="caps">COLUMBIA</hi>
                 <lb/>
                
                <hi rend="caps">COLLEGE OF ARTS AND SCIENCE</hi>
                 <lb/>
                <hi rend="caps">DEPARTMENT OF ENGLISH</hi> 
             </fw>
                
             <opener>   
                <dateline>Skyrim, 12-21-'58</dateline>
                
                
                <salute>Dear Bower and Lucile:</salute>
             </opener>
                <p>My feeling for you is a year-around one, and needs no emphasis at Xmas. I'm glad you are in the world.</p>
                
                <p>I'll be writing soon.</p>
                <closer>
                <salute>Affectionately,</salute>
                <signed>John Neihardt</signed> 
                </closer>
                
                <postscript><p>We've made two kinescopes, and will make another in January.</p></postscript>      
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
